{"tid":1422804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［拆局］中共派出福建幫嘅陰謀","createTime":"2019-08-06T12:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:38:35.000Z","uid":21678,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ad20f72fa2c15251f232d79d699bcc28b0e0f62b","tid":1422804,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"分而治之<br />\n一直係中共嘅管治手法<br />\n<br />\n大家須知道<br />\n香港呢兩個月嘅新聞<br />\n響大陸社交媒體基本上係被冷處理<br />\n就算係人民日報嘅官方帖<br />\n都會停止咗留言功能<br />\n唔畀人民理性討論<br />\n<br />\n但係今日大陸罕有地傳揚緊琴晚荃灣事件嘅相<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wrudrze.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWrudrze.png&h=e393b53b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上便呢幅受害者嘅相<br />\n唔單止可以響微博出現冇被河蟹<br />\n相反仲上咗熱搜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8mTBpou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8mTBpou.png&h=d909c920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個「漏網之魚」post <br />\n引起咗我嘅注意<br />\n正所謂識睇睇留言...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iai9Kov.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiai9Kov.png&h=b0aec641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mjd2jWR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmjd2jWR.png&h=bb0f16db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一望到留言即刻明哂<br />\n<br />\n琴晚嘅福建黑幫同元朗事件唔同嘅地方<br />\n就係佢哋可以<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>被用嚟挑起民族情緒</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n換言之呢班福建叔父<br />\n係被安排嚟「畀香港人打」嘅<br />\n目的就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>激起國內其他省份敵視香港人<br />\n以此阻止香港輸出革命！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以嚟緊嘅示威日子<br />\n應該會有更多呢類刀手出動<br />\n快閃斬人然後畀武勇派打至重傷<br />\n甚至被人打死！<br />\n<br />\n只有咁樣先可以將香港人同其他省份嘅人<br />\n放響絕對嘅對立面<br />\n從內部阻止示威蔓延上去！"},{"pid":"bf5d2b2e5897533def8f8fdbd46000f1419e2b31","tid":1422804,"uid":24345,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"亦可以證明今日有個巴打講嗰班福建佬同示威者都係中撚咗計喺北角撞正"},{"pid":"c1cf06fafc7107f5ab0905fb5efbd39e50315164","tid":1422804,"uid":237133,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:03:28.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"538eb5ba12507e8ffd4f0136e0f92391fe355e7c","tid":1422804,"uid":237133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:04:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e86081cf491670d0a7588ae4bb618c432501e31","tid":1422804,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:05:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"492b14bbeee2f5036889bbb732035d523eef50df","tid":1422804,"uid":245441,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"話斬傷左果個係香港人 祖籍廣東/廣西<br />\n分化其他省。"},{"pid":"1b6288c942a0a3685557dd166e3545f90e6acf91","tid":1422804,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"492b14bbeee2f5036889bbb732035d523eef50df","tid":1422804,"uid":245441,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"話斬傷左果個係香港人 祖籍廣東/廣西<br />\n分化其他省。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:07:15.000Z","msg":"呢個應該唔關事<br />\n佢純粹係唔好彩，咁啱行過呢度"},{"pid":"f5917d9fe6e92445b1f2a322d25464656edf7ca9","tid":1422804,"uid":273319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c53f70449b51809bd86f11ca473bd0d9512742a9","tid":1422804,"uid":296506,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"492b14bbeee2f5036889bbb732035d523eef50df","tid":1422804,"uid":245441,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"話斬傷左果個係香港人 祖籍廣東/廣西<br />\n分化其他省。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:10:37.000Z","msg":"混血兒...混省...哈哈..."},{"pid":"1e59da1620dc490d884971b5c2626a33fac77ae6","tid":1422804,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"佢哋思想真係好單純<br />\n完全俾人控制住佢哋諗乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx